  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of BGS649 in Male Obese Subjects With Hypogonadotropic Hypogonadism</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase IIb Multicentre, Double-Blind, Dose-Ranging, Randomised, Placebo-Controlled Study Evaluating Safety and Efficacy of BGS649 in Male Obese Subjects With Hypogonadotropic Hypogonadism</official_title>
  <sponsors>
